HEADWORD: Loriot
<hw>Lo"ri*ot</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr. OF.
<ets>loriou</ets>, for <ets>l'oriol</ets>, <ets>oriol</ets>,
<ets>l'</ets> being the article. The same word as <ets>oriole</ets>. See
<er>Oriole</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The golden oriole of
